This is the ConsumerServer Play Application
--------------------------------------------

To run:
1. Enter your Kafka server info into /conf/server.info:
	-first line: zookeeper hostname:port
	-second line: kafka hostname	
	-third line: kafka port 

2. Deploy this application onto any server (eg. Heroku, visit https://www.playframework.com/documentation/2.5.x/ProductionHeroku)

3. Frontend client can access your server at the public server url from step 2
